The lattice parameters ‘a and c’ of WSe2 film was found to be a = 3.325 and c = 12.921 Å, respectively. These values are in good agreement with the earlier reported value (Hankare et al. 2009a, 2010; Gayathri et al. 2012; Sathe et al. 2010). The average crystallite size was calculated using Scherrer formula:2D=Kλβcosθ,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
